<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Students may qualify for advanced standing (maximum of thirty hours) by submitting acceptable scores as recommended by the American Council On Education (ACE) on the College Board's Advanced Placement Program (AP). Grades and quality points are not given for advanced standing credit. Students will not be allowed to duplicate credit in any of the sections or transfer credit.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.bethelu.edu/academics/university_registrar/catalogs/" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
